        {
            "title": "美伊停火協議存疑 亞洲股市謹慎觀望",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/.130ucTWhmOBTs8AJXOEJw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA9Q076_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 週四亞洲股市在窄幅區間內波動,投資者對美國與伊朗之間脆弱的停火協議日益懷疑,同時油價反彈也令市場保持警惕。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">繼前一交易日大幅上漲後,區域市場基本陷入停滯,而ESM26下跌0.2%,原因是巴基斯坦斡旋的美伊停火協議條款不確定性增加。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">油價從本週的跌勢中反彈,因霍爾木茲海峽這一關鍵航運通道實際上仍被伊朗封鎖,幾乎沒有重新開放的跡象。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>伊朗停火協議存疑 亞洲股市陷入停滯</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">南韓KOSPI指數成為亞洲表現最差的市場,因晶片股回吐漲幅而下跌1.3%,而日本日經225指數和東證指數分別下跌0.4%和0.6%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-7a9ba0a3-89a7-39b7-ab36-76aa2d793e20-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國滬深300指數和上證綜合指數均下跌約0.5%,而香港恆生指數下跌0.5%,受阿里巴巴集團(HK:9988)拖累,該股下跌3%,此前Jefferies下調了其目標價。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">伊朗表示停火談判\"不合理\",同時以色列繼續對黎巴嫩發動攻擊,亞洲股市因此失去動力。伊朗官員要求將黎巴嫩納入最近的停火提案,但美國和以色列基本上拒絕了這一要求。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">伊朗還被視為繼續封鎖霍爾木茲海峽,這是亞洲石油和天然氣供應的關鍵航運通道,報導顯示自停火協議宣布以來,只有少數船隻通過該海峽。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國和伊朗官員將於本週稍後在巴基斯坦會面,但他們的會談主要議程以及停火協議的更多細節仍不明朗。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">華僑銀行分析師指出,儘管停火消息最初引發了風險偏好上升,\"但脆弱的談判和揮之不去的地緣政治風險\"限制了進一步上漲空間。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他們還指出,霍爾木茲海峽的石油流動將在未來幾天成為市場焦點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">週四亞洲市場整體表現猶豫不決,投資者對伊朗戰爭保持高度謹慎。大多數區域市場仍在消化3月份的大幅虧損。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">新加坡海峽時報指數下跌0.3%,而澳洲ASX 200指數持平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">印度Nifty 50指數期貨小幅下跌,此前該指數週三上漲近4%。印度是受伊朗戰爭導致石油和天然氣供應中斷影響最嚴重的國家之一。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E4%BC%8A%E5%81%9C%E7%81%AB%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0%E5%AD%98%E7%96%91-%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2%E8%82%A1%E5%B8%82%E8%AC%B9%E6%85%8E%E8%A7%80%E6%9C%9B-035644967.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-09 12:07:56",
