            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "郎咸平13万租出尖沙咀名鑄3房！9年前8,700萬買入 享1.8厘租金回報",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">豪宅市場租務暢旺，有名人業主趁機將名下豪宅出租。國際知名經濟學家<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"郎咸平\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:郎咸平;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/郎咸平\">郎咸平</a>新近租出尖沙咀<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"名鑄\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:名鑄;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4c0xud1\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">名鑄</a>一個3房海景戶，月租13萬元，呎租約58元，租金回報約1.8厘。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">更多消息：</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"譚仔家族又蝕讓名鑄 「六哥」3,380萬沽兩房勁蝕逾9球｜夠買1,309,495隻土匪雞翼\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:譚仔家族又蝕讓名鑄 「六哥」3,380萬沽兩房勁蝕逾9球｜夠買1,309,495隻土匪雞翼;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4ssyKKT\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">譚仔家族又蝕讓名鑄 「六哥」3,380萬沽兩房勁蝕逾9球｜夠買1,309,495隻土匪雞翼</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"米蘭站姚君達6,700萬沽名鑄 內地客曾開價1.75億拒賣 今帳蝕近390萬！夠買幾多個小廢包？\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:米蘭站姚君達6,700萬沽名鑄 內地客曾開價1.75億拒賣 今帳蝕近390萬！夠買幾多個小廢包？;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4dC4yJA\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">米蘭站姚君達6,700萬沽名鑄 內地客曾開價1.75億拒賣 今帳蝕近390萬！夠買幾多個小廢包？</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">消息指，郎咸平及相關人士名下的名鑄高層59樓E室，實用面積2,258平方呎，採3房3套間隔，大廳呈圓弧形型，設落地玻璃窗，享180度開揚維港海景，新近以每月13萬元租出，呎租約57.5元，較2024年月租13.5萬元輕微回調4%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-2492c040-284e-3684-830a-ceedfbc69a2a-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"28Hse網站同類租盤\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"518\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/TRXjvQkMSzFv_3etRyGgWw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUxOA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/3ffadd49a22d2a236a9b0001ea1a3405\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">28Hse網站同類租盤</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">28Hse網站同類租盤</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">翻查資料，郎咸平及相關人士於2017年5月以8,700萬元一手購入該單位，呎價約38,530元。以最新租金計，僅享約1.8厘租金回報。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">名鑄由新世界及市建局發展，坐落於尖沙咀河內道18號，有出口連接尖沙咀港鐵站，是一個集購物商場K11、五星級凱悅酒店及豪宅於一身的綜合發展項目。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">名鑄住宅部分建於27樓至頂層67樓，提供345個單位，內有38伙特色戶，包括相連及複式單位，面積816至5,260平方呎，高層可眺望維港煙花海景，吸引眾多名人業主入駐，包括米蘭站創辦人姚君達、中文大學校長盧煜明、騰訊副總裁姚曉光、祥益地產總裁汪敦敬等。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"28Hse網站同類租盤\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"645\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/GJl4TnAxF8P__5j3HEAIYQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0NQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/7cf46eaf9ed8f2e1f204316155434334\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">28Hse網站同類租盤</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">28Hse網站同類租盤</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據28Hse網站資料，名鑄近期平均成交呎價為31,700元，較3個月前升約9%；近期平均成交呎租約52元，近3個月錄得8宗成交，平均租金回報約2厘。屋苑現時共<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"26個單位放租\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:26個單位放租;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4vyWOP0\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">26個單位放租</a>，其中一間為郎咸平同類單位的<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"高層E室\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:高層E室;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4dCYHUb\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">高層E室</a>，連雅緻裝修，叫租15萬元。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"28Hse網站同類租盤\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"645\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/l1P_aPbSiilF97OFVUDY3A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0NQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/d5f3f1997bc4d6ad54960ca4e32fded0\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">28Hse網站同類租盤</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">28Hse網站同類租盤</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">延伸閱讀: <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"尖沙咀\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:尖沙咀;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/尖沙咀-27386\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">尖沙咀</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">延伸閱讀:</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">* <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"新聞連結\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:新聞連結;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/news/%E9%83%8E%E5%92%B8%E5%B9%B313%E4%B8%87%E7%A7%9F%E5%87%BA%E5%B0%96%E6%B2%99%E5%92%80%E5%90%8D%E9%91%843%E6%88%BF-9%E5%B9%B4%E5%89%8D8-700%E8%90%AC%E8%B2%B7%E5%85%A5-%E4%BA%AB1-8%E5%8E%98%E7%A7%9F%E9%87%91%E5%9B%9E%E5%A0%B1-75439\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">新聞連結</a>。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">* <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"28Hse App\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:28Hse App;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/appdownload\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">28Hse App</a>。</p></div>",
