        {
            "title": "黃金價格小幅下跌 交易員關注中東局勢再起波瀾",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/sJrODyAzwSFd_d9FhJhNpg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA5M0AC_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 週四亞洲交易時段,黃金價格小幅下跌,此前一個交易日僅錄得微幅上漲。投資者密切關注中東局勢再度緊張,這可能危及美國與伊朗之間脆弱的停火協議。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至美國東部時間21:30(北京時間01:30),現貨黃金下跌0.3%至4,704.96美元/盎司,而美國黃金期貨下跌1%至4,731.84美元/盎司。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">週三黃金收高0.3%,盤中一度上漲3%,因美國與伊朗之間的臨時停火協議緩解了即時供應衝擊擔憂,但未能完全平復市場。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-8499ee42-c477-3d0a-ad59-f32d12575471-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這項由巴基斯坦斡旋的停火協議為期兩週,旨在停止敵對行動並重新開放關鍵的霍爾木茲海峽。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市場情緒依然謹慎,因以色列對黎巴嫩的襲擊仍在繼續,令人質疑停火協議的持久性。伊朗表示,在目前情況下與美國進行和平談判是\"不合理的\"。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">伊朗官員警告稱,持續的襲擊破壞了信任,可能導致計劃中的談判脫軌,凸顯出在停火框架及其執行方面存在深刻分歧。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">週四油價溫和反彈,此前一個交易日因停火協議宣布而大幅下跌。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">黃金傳統上被視為避險資產,但一直受到油價飆升的壓力,油價上漲引發了全球通脹擔憂。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">投資者正密切關注將於週五公布的美國3月消費者物價指數(CPI)數據,預計該數據將進一步明確通脹前景和聯準會的政策路徑。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市場正在為顯著上升做準備,因近期石油衝擊帶來的能源驅動型價格壓力仍在經濟中逐步顯現。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與此同時,美元在前一交易日下跌0.7%後企穩,限制了黃金的進一步漲幅。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在其他貴金屬方面,白銀價格下跌1.3%至73.16美元/盎司,而鉑金下跌0.9%至2,011.14美元/盎司。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%BB%83%E9%87%91%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC%E5%B0%8F%E5%B9%85%E4%B8%8B%E8%B7%8C-%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E5%93%A1%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8%E4%B8%AD%E6%9D%B1%E5%B1%80%E5%8B%A2%E5%86%8D%E8%B5%B7%E6%B3%A2%E7%80%BE-023628227.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-09 10:53:06",
